# Engagement workspaces live here. Each is its own subdirectory:
#
#   agent/engagements/<name>/
#     scope.json         — authorized targets + out-of-scope rules
#     intel.md           — accumulated knowledge during the engagement
#     notes.md           — running log for the operator
#     findings/          — per-finding markdown reports
#     artifacts/         — captured request/response evidence, screenshots
#     reports/           — generated executive summary + technical report
#
# The contents of individual engagements are NOT committed by default.
# See ../../.gitignore.
